## Custom variations

To generate multiple variations you can use the generic @mixin <%= link_to 'mars-build-components','documentation/builders/mars-build-components' %>, visit the page on the builder to better understand how it works and arguments.

<% example_html do %>
<span class="badge">Badge</span>
<span class="badge-primary">Primary</span>
<span class="badge-success">Success</span>
<span class="badge-warning">Warning</span>
<% end %>


