## Create new variations

We can extend to generate new types of badge using the same stylized elements

<% example_html do %>
<span class="badge-pill">Badge</span>
<span class="badge-pill-primary">Primary</span>
<span class="badge-pill-success">Success</span>
<span class="badge-pill-warning">Warning</span>
<% end %>


